analysis_plan.correction_hint:
Execute profiling queries to check existence of early-terminated leases with actual_end_date_sk and customers from those leases appearing in fact_loan_contracts with later origination dates. Suggested queries:
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM fact_leasing_contracts WHERE early_termination_flag = TRUE AND actual_end_date_sk IS NOT NULL;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT customer_sk) FROM fact_leasing_contracts WHERE early_termination_flag = TRUE AND actual_end_date_sk IS NOT NULL;
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM fact_leasing_contracts l JOIN fact_loan_contracts ln ON l.customer_sk = ln.customer_sk AND ln.origination_date_sk > l.actual_end_date_sk WHERE l.early_termination_flag = TRUE AND l.actual_end_date_sk IS NOT NULL;
